items.title: Awesome Pascal
items.content_text:
### Logging

*   [jachLog (⭐51)](https://github.com/jachguate/jachLogMgr). `[Delphi]` pure pascal, flexible, extensible and lightweight library to add logging capabilities to your Delphi applications. Multiple log destinations supported. The library supports multithreaded applications and is itself multithreaded to minimize the impact writing the log may have on the performance on mission critical applications.
items.content_html:
Logging

  • jachLog (⭐51). [Delphi] pure pascal, flexible, extensible and lightweight library to add logging capabilities to your Delphi applications. Multiple log destinations supported. The library supports multithreaded applications and is itself multithreaded to minimize the impact writing the log may have on the performance on mission critical applications.

items.title: Awesome Gbdev
items.content_text:
### Homebrews / Syntax highlighting packages

*   [Homebrew Hub](https://hh.gbdev.io) - A community-led attempt to collect, archive and preserve every unlicensed and homebrew game released for Game Boy. Entries are playable online.

### Reverse Engineering / Syntax highlighting packages

*   [DMA hijacking](https://gbdev.io/guides/dma_hijacking) - A simple technique that allows you to run custom code in most GB/SGB/CGB games, provided you have an ACE exploit.
